{"id": 2743, "genre": 1001, "title": "习惯了线上聊天，面对面交流你都有哪些不适应？", "description": "在微信上可以长篇大论，一到口头聊天瞬间社恐。（题图来自：iStock ©️nuvolanevicata ）", "record_count": 3142, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20190118135649mJqOSVzlUxKrXsuk.jpeg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2019-01-24T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 324352, "content": "习惯于线上聊天，当着面竟然不敢直视他人的眼睛！", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 970221}, {"id": 328961, "content": "眼对眼", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1415383}, {"id": 324353, "content": "对面这话痨见面这么沉默让我不适", "image": null, "praise_count": 19, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1023476}, {"id": 324354, "content": "面对面时只能Freestyle了，不能撤回删除了！", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 970221}, {"id": 324355, "content": "做不到表情包那样丰富的表情和内心戏，还要说着自以为幽默的话，结果经常冷场", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1559267}, {"id": 327940, "content": "眼睛不知道看哪里，盯久了又尴尬。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1058013}, {"id": 324356, "content": "不适应不能发表情了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1401626}, {"id": 325124, "content": "话题突然聊完 并且还没开启下个话题的时候 不可以放下手机装消失", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 315533}, {"id": 324357, "content": "尴尬时候不能发表情包", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1553583}, {"id": 324869, "content": "没有足够的时间思考，无法查询某些资料，不能正确表达自己的想法。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1566507}, {"id": 324358, "content": "我不喜欢秒回", "image": null, "praise_count": 36, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1557107}, {"id": 324359, "content": "自己的表情包不够浪", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1566548}, {"id": 324360, "content": "不能问“在吗”……", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 982279}, {"id": 324361, "content": "跟别人互动发现有很多尴尬并且没办法用表情包敷衍过去", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1544940}, {"id": 324362, "content": "忍不住要玩手机。假装很投入地，一边说话一边搜寻下一个话题，很累！", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1565768}, {"id": 324363, "content": "没有办法讲的很清楚，觉得思维都慢了", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1566581}, {"id": 324364, "content": "半生不熟的人最麻烦。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1513949}, {"id": 324365, "content": "要配合表情", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1566582}, {"id": 324366, "content": "控制表情", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1497432}, {"id": 324367, "content": "完全没有", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1054974}, {"id": 324368, "content": "其实还好，因为我线上也不咋聊", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 821455}, {"id": 324369, "content": "讲话时不知道我该用什么表情，然后很尴尬，不自由", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1565947}, {"id": 324371, "content": "不能随时AFK。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1061312}, {"id": 324372, "content": "不知道说点什么", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1541584}, {"id": 325140, "content": "不知道说什么。很快就冷场", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1570424}, {"id": 324373, "content": "不能玩手机了也。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1061312}, {"id": 324375, "content": "面对面，撒谎都不从容自然了，哈哈哈哈", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1566603}, {"id": 324632, "content": "不能百度话术", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1567408}, {"id": 326680, "content": "突然不知该说啥", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1574649}, {"id": 324377, "content": "我还是喜欢面对面，如果可以的话", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1563769}, {"id": 324379, "content": "不能“认真”的“听”一个人说完，另一个人再说", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1546558}, {"id": 324381, "content": "面聊不熟悉的人容易尴尬", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1472670}, {"id": 324382, "content": "你有来言，我就得有去语", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 596413}, {"id": 326942, "content": "同样的话，面对面交流会有不同的语气，避免不了尴尬", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1578105}, {"id": 323359, "content": "开玩笑说了句俏皮话之后想要亲自比出狗头", "image": null, "praise_count": 73, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 324383, "content": "不能发表情包+1😂", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1340666}, {"id": 323360, "content": "跟人面对面聊天时也很想丢出表情包回应", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 326432, "content": "不知道说什么，挺尴尬的。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1576599}, {"id": 323361, "content": "别人讲了个不是很好笑的段子，发现并不能用哈哈哈来掩饰过去", "image": null, "praise_count": 449, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 324385, "content": "要盯着对方眼睛开，躲避会显得不自然，但一直盯着我也会不自然", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 58260}, {"id": 327970, "content": "对喜欢的人说不出口", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1586193}, {"id": 324386, "content": "会尴尬沉默", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1566661}, {"id": 323363, "content": "在线上讨论问题时还可以斟酌一下查查资料，面对面可没这反应时间", "image": null, "praise_count": 244, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 324387, "content": "不能假装没看见", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1565166}, {"id": 324388, "content": "感觉更好，不喜欢线上聊天，喜欢面对面交流。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1081700}, {"id": 324390, "content": "不知道说什么了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1483531}, {"id": 324391, "content": "面对面看着就很尴尬..", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1564606}, {"id": 324648, "content": "缺少自信了，并且没有时间想象和打草稿了...", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1567429}, {"id": 324649, "content": "思考的时间短了些，俏皮话少了些", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1454392}, {"id": 324394, "content": "没有狗头表情不方便。对不那么熟悉的人很容易就开始了尬聊。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1428289}]}